{"tid":1831954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊用Google Photos幫手足（2）","createTime":"2020-01-20T22:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T01:54:28.000Z","uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d891e346c0dfefab26becb5c229274cc82a7f6cd","tid":1831954,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:12:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1822864/page/4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1822864/page/4</a><br />\n<br />\n上回講到，大家可以用Google Photos幫手足，但問題我一個人找相，Save 相係無用，最好係大家各自搵，然後不定期Zip起，上載到匿名分享檔案嘅網站（最好係14日後自動Delete），大家互相喺度Share，就可以分散得嚟建立到一個更加強大嘅Database。<br />\n<br />\n每套相都要寫關於啲乜，邊度嚟，乜嘢事件之類，咁樣大家就更容易捉到班愛字頭嘅真面目。"},{"pid":"d9e2fb561e8e5c180948ba96a6aac8fca74018af","tid":1831954,"uid":303020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:18:20.000Z","msg":"唔錯！"},{"pid":"d9f4e5c080a1b6421cfa38b35c71830c2d2fbfc5","tid":1831954,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:18:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc4569eb4bc24805e5ccbc09c370ded2d496755","tid":1831954,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:18:52.000Z","msg":"手足好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690b7223f522a2104830811a823a1c25f4cde3ed","tid":1831954,"uid":193494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f41e8a57c35aebfd4f6c3a40b670c356f1fdf6ae","tid":1831954,"uid":306028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T00:07:50.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"597a2d1330a5df485a1a746a3ec3b76c2407c218","tid":1831954,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"點解咁有用嘅嘢無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{